Naitae artifact LICENSE
===========================

This artifact consists of several components, each by its own license.
Modifications made for this work inherit the license of the component they modify.

1. jdk21-4-rv/ — modified OpenJDK 21 that implements Naitae.
   All new and modified code related to Naitae in OpenJDK 21 are Licensed under the GNU General Public License version 2 only, with the Classpath Exception (GPLv2+CE), as in the upstream OpenJDK. Please view jdk21-4-rv/LICENSE and jdk21-4-rv/ADDITIONAL_LICENSE_INFO for more details.

2. env/agents/ — prebuilt RV tool jars (JavaMOP/TraceMOP/Valg, and LazyMOP).
   These are compiled from the TraceMOP(JavaMOP and Valg) and LazyMOP projects and retains the upstream license of the project it was built from. 
   
3. experiments/ and env/ — the evaluation harness, scripts, and Dockerfile.
   Released under the MIT License (below).

